description:
Reality TV star & RIDICULOUSNESS co-host Chanel West Coast joins the boys to talk about her friends trying to escape the friend zone, why she gave Logan the wrong number, and how she developed her friendship with Rob Dyrdek. The squad also invites Chanel’s neighbor number, Joel, to the set, because he happened to be in LA... what a small, creepy, world.
